      "content": "I checked the supplier manifest and the shipment is definitely delayed by at least three weeks. So we're definitely going to run out if we don't hide them soon. I just don't want us to get slammed with refund requests later. If we keep them \"In Stock\", we're basically lying to people, right? Or is there a way to handle this without losing the sales momentum?",
